<section class="aboutus-header">
    <h1>About Quality Copiers & Printers</h1>
    <p>Your reliable partner in office automation solutions since 2007.</p>
</section>


<section class="aboutus-profile">
    <img src="~/images/aboutUs_image1.png" alt="About us page image to change" />

    <div class="text-content">
    <br />
    <h2>Company Profile</h2>
    <p>Quality Copiers was established more than fifteen years ago and has<br />
        been under new ownership since October 2007. Our CEO has more than <br />
        thirty years of experience in the office automation industry and has worked <br />for
        two of the industry giants until an opportunity afforded him to purchase <br />this company.</p>

    <br />

    <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
    <p>Our goal is to supply reliable, honest and cost effective service to 
        all our <br />clients. Quality Copiers provides technical support, machine 
        sales and <br />consumable sales for office automation equipment. Our clients 
        range from small to corporate companies, which also include copier dealers.</p>

    <br />
    <h2>Our Expertise</h2>
    <p>Our specialty is Ricoh/Gestetner printers and copiers, but we have<br />
        experience in servicing and maintaining various other brands like 
        HP-<br />Hewlett Packard, Xerox, Minolta, Epson, Canon and many others.</p>
      <br />
      <br />
